"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"第一步：\\n\\n领取 NFT 链接：\\n\\n[https://galaxy.eco/perp/campaign/GCGRYUUwnX ](https://galaxy.eco/perp/campaign/GCGRYUUwnX)\\n\\n以太坊L2 Optimistic\\n\\n任务内容    在 Perp v2（Op）上有至少 100 USDC 的交易量（使用 10 USDC 开 10 倍杠杆也算，至少充值11U比较保险）\\n\\n用跳桥从polygon转eth到op  交互了跳桥，而且费用低，跳桥费用转过去4u大概\\n\\n[https://app.hop.exchange/](https://app.hop.exchange/)\\n\\neth到了op之后，去找弹弓做个交互 用eth买usdc   这样交互了弹弓\\n\\n[https://app.slingshot.finance/trade/o/USDC](https://app.slingshot.finance/trade/o/USDC)\\n\\n然后到项目链接     存usdc进去\\nhttps://app.perp.com/\\n\\n然后开单\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XX47hg-teHtcC6IoXswCy.png?height=512&width=380)\\n\\n开单后  记得再平掉    然后搞定\\n\\n到领取NFT链接看\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/A7z-X6gdD8J1tBEs4Efsl.png?height=472&width=867)\\n\\n第二个不说了 \\n\\n第三个做的时候我bsc没钱了  用  movr平台才从op转到polygon  走的也是跳桥  交互了2个\\n\\n[https://app.fund.movr.network/](https://app.fund.movr.network/)\\n\\n等会再找polygon到bsc的链\",\"timestamp\":1640412769,\"title\":\"驯鹿nft\"},\"digest\":\"cXl3eaTYjDmQVTSWHcfxTQIrCurqZGpj3WdaUXDNI9Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2145814E43A49844d7F03a4d00FC240C7C8e329B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hlVaqnWetXNLOdbUcrmT6zqhD-sSiyeNgbGQgW11eV4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8vb0QasgWY_R-HHXATDV8uMW4NJA_mIccBkyvaZX7NA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BqzQL5kjLYg5y7WEaxn8KtuOukveS7x4XScA4GPWtqyT3zeHe17DiNrmtHeGzq5OiiXeiTcJftKTBg1EeLcNqw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x36750ab47e2bd18476d83a573efc63e6f5cd5af960619d2b844954c57f2cb72007c8813b99cbd749ef4f8d23f422e59d7a6d8a387c391d5b5cea7c7393df45711b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hlVaqnWetXNLOdbUcrmT6zqhD-sSiyeNgbGQgW11eV4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8vb0QasgWY_R-HHXATDV8uMW4NJA_mIccBkyvaZX7NA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"n